Package com.epam.training.bean

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Build
    Class Build is a Java Bean that stores the data of project's builds available in the application (id, name, project in which this build is found).
    Entity
    Abstract Class Entity is a Java Bean that is a superclass to all other entity classes (Member, Issue, Project, etc.).
    Feature
    Class Feature is a Java Bean that stores the data of all issues' features available in the application (status, type, priority, resolution).
    Issue
    Class Issue is a Java Bean that stores the data of issues reported in the application (id, summary, description, status, priority, type, project, assignee, etc.).
    Member
    Class Member is a Java Bean that stores the data of application members (id, login and password, full name, etc.).
    Project
    Class Project is a Java Bean that stores the data of projects registered in the application (id, name, description, project's manager).
